{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-20", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "誠摯邀請", "storyInfo": "曼弗雷德用飛空艇做誘餌消滅大公爵主力的計劃破產。W和赫德雷救下了跳船的伊內絲，三人再次團聚。而變形者集群也找上了阿米婭。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g11_hispdwarshipdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老威靈頓幾乎把他所有的預備戰艦都派過來了？", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，公爵閣下。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威靈頓公爵似乎對那艘船......勢在必得。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的前鋒部隊應該已經與薩卡茲交火了。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，還有開斯特......", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那女人幾乎從來不走出她的防區，這次連她都坐不住了......", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘會飛的小船到底有多吸引人，值得他們這麼大費周章？", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您的參謀們同樣建議您盡可能地獲得那艘飛空艇的技術，公爵閣下。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是抗衡薩卡茲，還是將來面對......其他可能的對手，這種前所未有的武器都能為我們爭取到更多的空間。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓他們閉嘴。什麼可能的對手？他們這是在教唆我分裂維多利亞。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來這裡只是為了接戴菲恩回家的。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "參謀們說，諾伯特區的情況，可能會很糟糕......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩不會有事，她可是我的女兒。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_241", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公、公爵閣下......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒告訴過你們嗎？不允許在艦內奔跑。", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_241", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看，那個移動地塊的影子......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_241", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像......有些不太對......", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫德米爾公爵接過副官遞給自己的望遠鏡。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被朝陽拉長的地塊影子中，投影出的卻不是諾伯特區的樣貌。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為建築物的遮擋嗎？溫德米爾思考著，是有些奇怪，像是一座塔。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔？"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是......大廈？"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那是......碎片大廈的影子？", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能？這是一種自然現象嗎？還是......", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才說，開斯特和威靈頓的部隊還有多久能抵達這附近？", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕不會超過兩個小時......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是難得，三位公爵的軍隊，居然一起出現在這個地塊附近......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我們的參謀報告，其他幾位大公爵也同樣在蠢蠢欲動，他們要是真開動自己的戰艦出現在這裡也並不奇怪。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在部隊待了這麼多年，還從沒遇上過這樣的事。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#4$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停船！所有部隊馬上停下！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓他們馬上撤出這個地塊附近！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發射紅色信號彈，警告友軍！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快！快！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發送明碼電文，通告周圍的所有維多利亞部隊！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡可能會成為碎片大廈的攻擊地點！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好、好的！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘船不要轉向，向諾伯特區加速行進！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得在那風暴形成之前，找到戴菲恩！", "name": "溫德米爾公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_868_1#3$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g9_airshipdockcorridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一朵朵紅色信號彈在雲層之下炸起，扭曲的地塊陰影正在變回原狀。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很出色，伊內絲。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是一次並非全功率的試射，我們有很多可以選擇的地點。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我不得不承認，有一些小小的可惜。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但軍事委員會的計劃目標，從來就不止一個。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴食腐者之王閣下，準備進軍。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風暴會為他開路。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲常常提起，死亡也是工具。"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她有時會向赫德雷自嘲，自己可能已經習慣死人的身份了。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過等到死亡真的來臨，伊內絲發現，自己比想像的要平靜得多。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她閉上了眼睛。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猛然，火光與熱量撲面而來，伴隨著的，還有強烈的衝擊波。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種炸藥的味道，伊內絲很熟悉。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她扯起嘴角。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爆炸的塵煙撲面而來，餘燼仍然帶著火的溫度。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些餘燼在聚集，在飄舞，在編織。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的歷史由餘燼織就，但有的時候，這些塵埃也能編織出些別的東西。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如......"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲栽入一團輕柔的煙塵之中。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餘燼形成的巨網托住了她。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不該覺得......他們兩個能有什麼好主意的。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g10_wildbattlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，伊內絲，還活著嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種爆炸的難度很高，搞出什麼意外也不奇怪啦。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷，算了，直接埋了吧。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真是抱歉，姑且活著。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，掃興。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，喜歡我給你放的煙火嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猜猜我偷偷在你的衣服裡面縫上過什麼？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇！誰能想到，是個定位器耶！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你以為我沒發現嗎？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼粗的針腳，說真的，你的縫補手藝真夠差的。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁，原本是為了給你點真正的“驚喜”的，不過，好吧，這樣也行。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這些——", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們知不知道在戰場上保持衣服乾淨整潔有多不容易。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們居然就這麼把我丟進了一團燒著的灰裡面？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你以前還會形容我的源石技藝叫餘燼呢。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在沒這個心情。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你傷得不輕。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總比死了強。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼！赫德雷！你居然會用源石技藝嗎？我還以為你只會用刀砍人！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餘燼？怪不得我每次把炸彈扔你臉上你都好像沒什麼事！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你是不是不怕被炮打啊？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i08", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你是不是可以用灰揚別人一臉啊？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。", "name": "赫德雷"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你老是把自己弄得灰頭土臉，是不是這個源石技藝的副作用啊？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴。", "name": "赫德雷"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼。", "name": "伊內絲"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經多少年沒看過你這麼狼狽的樣子了，伊內絲？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我，你以後也不會再看到了。", "name": "伊內絲"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別對自己的運氣太有自信，搞不好回去的路上就撞上血魔大君在散步呢。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫德雷"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，我建議你換個比諭。", "name": "赫德雷"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，在曼弗雷德身邊待了那麼長時間，對王庭裡那些老怪物有感情了？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你該謝謝我！要不是我回來的路上遇到了遍地亂竄的你，說不定你已經又被你其他的老朋友抓走了呢！", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你真的很吵，我寧願回監獄裡去，至少安靜。", "name": "赫德雷"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請回，我可以主動向特雷西斯舉報你。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我們去哪？", "name": "伊內絲"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W的安全屋。", "name": "赫德雷"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我可以勉強當做是回家。", "name": "伊內絲"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有——", "name": "伊內絲"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......謝謝。", "name": "伊內絲"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我要回去。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她今天的腿腳怎麼那麼慢？是走路的時候摔傷了？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得去幫她一把，等把她接出來，這種救命之恩，肯定夠薛她幾瓶好酒了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愣著幹嘛，走啊！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，漢娜！諾伯特區如今是一片火海！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德又不是蠢蛋，她會躲著火走的。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她死了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？摩根，這不是開玩笑的——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說了！貝爾德死了！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#11$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒看到那把蝴蝶刀嗎，那把沾著血的蝴蝶刀！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#11$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是貝爾德從不離身的武器，不會有錯......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，這把刀在另一個人手裡，這就意味著......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定只是個誤會，說不定是貝爾德不小心把她的刀弄丟了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也會有粗心的時候，對吧？她也不是沒搞丟過東西。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年，她搞丟了我們一打羽獸蛋，記得嗎？本來我們早上是有煎蛋吃的。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她偶爾會大意一下，這沒什麼......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜......麥克拉倫拿著那把刀。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德最後就是去找他的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他聾了兩隻耳朵，大概是......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$2"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$2"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈！貝爾德和麥克拉倫多少年的交情了，你們是不是又在嚇我？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德就是把她的刀借給了麥克拉倫用一下嘛，沒什麼大不了的。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我們可以問問他情況，他也許會告訴我們，這只是個......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他人在哪？麥克拉倫和我們一起離開諾伯特區了，對吧？那就一定在這些人裡面。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問一下，不就能解開誤會了嘛......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麥克拉倫——你在哪——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麥克拉......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......漢娜，他聽不見。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要殺了他！！！我要殺了那個混帳！！！我要把他找出來，抽出他的每塊骨頭！！！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜！......行了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜！你*維多利亞粗口*是不是早就知道？！你為什麼不去——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼不去敲碎他的腦袋為貝爾德報仇？！你以為我不想嗎？！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#7$2"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我不想嗎！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#7$2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這*維多利亞粗口*沒意義！幹掉一個嚇瘋了的聾子沒有一點意義！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#7$2"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漢娜，我恨透了這些，我恨透了這些東西，我是個徹頭徹尾的蠢貨，自以為是的傻瓜！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛，貝爾德......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$2"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不參與這些事，她們也許就不會......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我到底是為了什麼回來？！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為我是為了什麼回來？！", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#10$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是不是......從一開始，就是個因為虛假的責任心而犯下的錯誤？"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己內心中怎麼看待她們，看待這些曾一起出生入死，一起歷盡磨難的友人？"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是......這份她無比珍視的“友情”，其實不過是個連自己都騙過了的說辭？"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是，就連自己，都開始漸漸地把自己看作是一位國王？"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賞賜慈悲，播撒仁義......然後，收取希望與敬仰。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己到底......想成為什麼？"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己到底期待成為什麼？"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......維娜，我們回來，是因為我們沒有辦法忍受......只是在一邊旁觀。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這是我們的街道，我們的區塊，我們的國家。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你總是衝鋒在前，但這不是你的責任。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們跟在你身後，也不是因為期待你成為怎樣的人。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，你只是我們的維娜，對吧。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當然。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只會是維娜，我發誓。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$2"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_battlefield", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要把這些諾伯特區的市民帶去哪裡？總不能讓他們在荒野上自生自滅吧？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，這裡是戰場的中心。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果這些市民願意的話，他們可以去我母親的領地裡生活。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#10$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母親她開了一座移動城市到倫蒂尼姆附近，雖然只是小型的要塞城市，但安置這些人還是沒問題的。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡鐸爾，你有什麼想法嗎？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#10$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩，你發現了嗎，自從你開始不再掩飾自己的身份，你說話的口氣都變了。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道貝爾德的事......讓你很難過。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都很難過，但你不需要在這個時候讓大家的心情變得更糟糕。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，總算找到人了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問，能為我們倒杯水嗎？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那條德拉克......我們不喜歡她的那些火，燒在身上難滅得很。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......變形者。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#3$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸，我們有日子沒見了吧？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來這裡幹什麼？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#3$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找水喝。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順便來正式和我們的這位小魔王打個招呼。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位女妖可是誇了你不少呢。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭，後退。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line370"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的，博士，雖然我從來沒有見過這位客人現在的樣貌......但我對他們很熟悉，他們在那些歷史中出現了很多次。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是他們總是游離在王庭之外，對除了自身之外的一切都......缺乏興趣。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者的碎片，你為什麼出現在我們面前？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你確實是貨真價實的魔王，小兔子。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那東西把你也折磨得不輕。你不是薩卡茲，真佩服你的小腦袋裡能裝下那麼多的東西。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶，我們最寶貴的東西，但有時候也會是我們的毒藥。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，我們似乎還是能有些共同話題的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......是不是也覺得我不配承載“魔王”這頂冠冕？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，那隻嘮叨的死魂靈狠狠罵了你一頓。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別理他，他從來不討人喜歡。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#9$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是一位古老的薩卡茲，您覺得......魔王需要怎麼做？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，是個好問題。我們沒當過，我們也並不在意......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們想，最起碼應該足夠強大？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "強大到......足夠跨越所有的猶豫和迷茫，對吧？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但有一點我們十分確定，你不該向我們提出這個問題，小魔王。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有很長的路要走。無論是繼續領著那個叫羅德島的組織打打鬧鬧，還是遵從薩卡茲眾魂的指引。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，抱歉，我們忘了，薩卡茲眾魂不會接納你，就像不會接納我們一樣。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都是異類。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過——", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你總會在未來的某一刻明白，你是無法戰勝時間的。我們的記憶中，每一任的魔王總會在最後走上同一條道路。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但那不會是我。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——拒絕走上那條道路。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不要急著否定我們，卡特斯。我們也曾以為另一位年輕的魔王會給我們驚喜，但似乎你們的命運依舊牢不可破。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#2$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們依然對你充滿了期待，一位不是薩卡茲的魔王......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位仍然不斷成長且質疑自己血脈的年輕魔王......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位我們都從未見過的魔王......", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你想幹什麼。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#3$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......並無惡意。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魔王，我們不敢宣揚我們比你更加具有智慧，我們也無法教會你任何事。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是想要發出一個邀請，請求一個能夠深入瞭解這樣一個......“唯一”個體的機會。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸，你要是和我們活得一樣長，你就會明白的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你眼前出現了一個從未見過的東西，怎麼可能忍住不去碰碰看呢？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊敬的魔王，請給我們漫長的生命一次驚喜。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}